import React from 'react'; import './TrackingDetails.css'; // Ensure you have a corresponding CSS file for styling const TrackingDetails = () => { const trackingDetails = { id: 'MC-2023-45678', date: 'Nov 16, 2023', time: '10:20 AM', status: 'In Transit', estimatedDelivery: 'Nov 18, 2023', detailedTracking: [ { event: 'Package Picked Up', date: 'Nov 15, 2023', time: '2:45 PM', location: 'New York, NY' }, { event: 'Arrived at Sorting Facility', date: 'Nov 15, 2023', time: '3:30 PM', location: 'Newark, NJ' }, { event: 'Departed Facility', date: 'Nov 15, 2023', time: '4:15 PM', location: 'Newark, NJ' }, { event: 'In Transit', date: 'Nov 16, 2023', time: '10:20 AM', location: 'Somewhere over the Atlantic' }, { event: 'Arrived at Distribution Hub', date: 'Nov 16, 2023', time: '11:45 AM', location: 'London, UK' }, { event: 'Out for Delivery', date: 'Nov 16, 2023', time: '1:30 PM', location: 'London, UK' }, { event: 'Delivered', date: 'Nov 16, 2023', time: '2:15 PM', location: 'London, UK' }, ], shipmentInfo: { serviceType: 'Standard Delivery', weight: '2.5 kg', dimensions: '12" x 8" x 4"', shipDate: 'Nov 15, 2023', recipient: 'John Doe', address: '123 Main Street, Apt 4B, New York, NY 10001', }, deliveryOptions: [ { option: 'Delay Delivery', description: 'Reschedule delivery for a later date.' }, { option: 'Signature Required', description: 'Ensure someone is available to sign for the package.' }, { option: 'Leave at Door', description: 'Allow the package to be left at the door if no one is available.' }, ], packageTravelMap: 'path-to-map-image.jpg', // Replace with actual image path }; return (

Tracking Details

ID: {trackingDetails.id}

Updated: {trackingDetails.date} - {trackingDetails.time}

Shipment Status

{trackingDetails.status}

Estimated Delivery: {trackingDetails.estimatedDelivery}

Detailed Tracking

    {trackingDetails.detailedTracking.map((event, index) => (
  • {event.event} - {event.date} {event.time} - {event.location}
    • ))}

Shipment Information

Service Type: {trackingDetails.shipmentInfo.serviceType}

Weight: {trackingDetails.shipmentInfo.weight}

Dimensions: {trackingDetails.shipmentInfo.dimensions}

Ship Date: {trackingDetails.shipmentInfo.shipDate}

Recipient: {trackingDetails.shipmentInfo.recipient}

Address: {trackingDetails.shipmentInfo.address}

Delivery Options

    {trackingDetails.deliveryOptions.map((option, index) => (
  • {option.option} - {option.description}
    • ))}

Package Travel Map

); }; export default TrackingDetails;
